different. This side investigation aims to answer/illustrate whether/how 
the sensor-to-sensor CRPIX difference depends on the CD matrix and field 
rotation.

If rotation *does* matter, I need to update my plots in the aforementioned
script and see how steady the CRPIX determination really is. If rotation
does *NOT* matter, the next thing to check is whether the discrepant cases
have something else, like significant skew (beyond a pure rotation matrix).

